NK040(thi)060:1: // ma cig gi bka' srung zangs ri'i btsan rgod spun gnyis kyi gtor chog bzhugs /
NK040(thi)060:2: yum chen d+aak+ki'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)060:3: ma cig gi bka' srung zangs ri'i btsan rgod sgrubs thabs las byang sbyor dngos rjes gsum ni /
NK040(thi)060:4: rnal 'byor pa gnyan sa ri khrod 'grims pa'i dus
NK040(thi)060:5: blo bur dgra byung zhing ting nge 'dzin gtor bas
NK040(thi)060:6: ltas ngan cho 'phrul blo bur btang bar 'dod na
NK040(thi)060:7: rin po che zangs ga mtshal dang ra khrag gi
NK040(thi)060:8: ling+ga dang sgrub gtor bca' bar byas la /
NK040(thi)060:10: rang nyid rje btsun ma bsgom pa'i spyi bor ma
NK040(thi)060:11: cig ma bskyed cing thugs ka'i dzahdamara po las 'od
NK040(thi)060:12: zer lcags kyu lta bur 'phros pas mdun du zangs
NK040(thi)060:13: ri'i btsan rgod sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag
NK040(thi)060:14: gnyis zangs kyi mdung dar bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)060:15: chibs su zangs rta dmar po la bcibs pa /
NK040(thi)060:16: sku la zangs khrabs gsol ba /
NK040(thi)060:17: dbu la zangs rmog bya ru btsugs pa /
NK040(thi)060:20: khyi dmar rol du khrid pa /
NK040(thi)060:21: bya dmar klad nas lding ba /
NK040(thi)060:22: de 'dra'i 'khor tshogs sprul pa dpag tu med pas phrin las sgrub par bsgom /
NK040(thi)060:25: tsa tri hur thum ma ra ya rbad phatah rbad sngags so //
NK040(thi)060:26: tsa tri hur thum dza tri nan /
NK040(thi)060:27: tsa tri hur thum tril rbad sod s+w+aa h+aah 'gugs pa gong du song bas 'dir /
NK040(thi)060:28: n+ri tri badz+ra ang+ku sha dza dzahmh'u bam hoh brjod la d+aa 'ur bcas /
NK040(thi)060:29: bden pa bdar gu gul bdug la gtor ma nya bo rnams bka' srung la mchod cing /
NK040(thi)060:30: ra tsa hur thum e dam b+ha ling+ta kha khi kh+aa hi /
NK040(thi)060:32: zangs ri mkhar dmar gyi dgon pa na //
NK040(thi)060:33: srog zan shan pa mched gnyis ni //
NK040(thi)060:34: btsan rgod 'bar ba mdung thung can //
NK040(thi)060:35: chibs su btsan rta dmar po bcibs //
NK040(thi)060:36: sku la bse khrab dmar po gsol //
NK040(thi)060:37: dbu la bswe rmog dmar po mnab //
NK040(thi)060:38: rmog phor bya rgod dang ru btsug /
NK040(thi)060:39: glad na bya dmar lings se ling //
NK040(thi)060:40: sngon na mi dmar brengs se breng //
NK040(thi)060:41: phyi nas khyi dmar khengs se kheng //
NK040(thi)060:42: btsan chas 'khor gsum khra la la //
NK040(thi)060:43: mdung dar dmar po lhabs se lhab //
NK040(thi)060:44: btsan rta dmar po zings se zing //
NK040(thi)060:45: btsan khyi dmar po khengs se kheng //
NK040(thi)060:46: btsan zhags dmar po rgyangs se rgyang //
NK040(thi)060:47: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK040(thi)060:48: sngon tshe yum gyi bka' lung bzhin //
NK040(thi)060:49: sdang byed dgra la rtag phyung cig /
NK040(thi)060:50: gnod byed bgegs la las mdzod cig /
NK040(thi)060:51: ri khrod 'grims pa'i mthun rkyen gyis //
NK040(thi)060:52: stong nyid bsgom pa'i yon bdag mdzod //
NK040(thi)060:53: mos gus can gyi bu slob skyongs //
NK040(thi)060:54: gnod cing 'tshe ba'i dgra bgegs thul //
NK040(thi)060:55: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK040(thi)060:56: tsa tri hur thum e dam b+ha ling+ta kha hi kh+aa hi /
NK040(thi)060:58: sngon tshe ma cig lab sgron spyan snga ru //
NK040(thi)060:62: 'di yan gtor 'bul nang nub byas na lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'ong ba'o //
NK040(thi)060:63: 'di man chad lhag ma'i gtor ma dgra phyogs su
NK040(thi)060:64: gru gsum nang du thun gyi brab cing ling+ga me
NK040(thi)060:65: la sregs / pha rol po'i sngags pa dang 'gras na bri thabs bsad sngags 'adi'o //
NK040(thi)060:66: tshes zhabs su mnan na gnyan /
NK040(thi)060:69: zangs ri mkhar dmar gyi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)060:70: btsan rgod 'bar ba mdung thung can //
NK040(thi)060:71: dgra la dmag sna drongs du gsol //
NK040(thi)060:72: dgra mkhar thog gis bsgyel du gsol //
NK040(thi)060:73: dgra yul ser bas da phud cig /
NK040(thi)060:74: dgra bo'i khang khyim than gyi khengs par gyis //
NK040(thi)060:75: dgra bo'i pha tshan da phyes shig /
NK040(thi)060:76: bu tsha ma tshan da phyes shig /
NK040(thi)060:77: dgra la gzer nad da thongs cig /
NK040(thi)060:78: dgra la zha grum da thong cig /
NK040(thi)060:79: snying gi sgo nga da chog cig /
NK040(thi)060:80: sems kyi mar me da sod cig /
NK040(thi)060:81: rgyug sgo dgra la da phyes shig /
NK040(thi)060:82: lo ro dgra la da phobs cig /
NK040(thi)060:83: ma cig lab sgron bka' lung bzhin //
NK040(thi)060:84: dam tshig tshul bzhin gnyer 'di gtad //
NK040(thi)060:85: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK040(thi)060:86: tsa tri hur thum tril rbad sod phatah ma cig
NK040(thi)060:87: bka' srung zangs ri btsan rgod kyis las byang 'bod
NK040(thi)060:88: rbad bsad gsum sngags dang bcas pa rdzogs so ////
